front.title: •Baron Soontir Fel
front.gametext: Adds 3 to power of anything he pilots. When piloting Saber 1, adds one battle destiny and 2 to maneuver. Adds 1 to your total battle destiny for each of your piloted TIE Interceptors in same battle.
front.lore: Corellian Baron. Leader of famed 181st Imperial Fighter Wing. Taught at the Imperial Academy on Prefsbelt IV. Instructed Biggs Darklighter.
